PSA: Please Don't Use SysId Before Manual Tuning Technical
Hi! In light of the many recent SysId help threads, I thought I’d put out this reminder that SysId is a supplemental tool intended to help fairly advanced users get the last bits of performance out of their mechanisms. SysId is not supposed to replace manual tuning, especially not for users who haven’t yet fully mastered it. If you cannot make sense of the SysId diagnostics panel, please: spend your time manually-tuning your mechanisms instead. It will teach you more, and get you good results…
